5.2 Communication Protocol

Your ACRS software communicates with the hardware via serial (RS-232/USB) using the following command protocol:

Command Format Response Description
Set Frequency SET_FREQ <Hz> OK or ACK Sets output frequency
Read Phase READ_PHASE -12.5 (float) Returns phase difference in degrees
Read Amplitude READ_AMP 2.45 (float) Returns amplitude in mV
Read Frequency READ_FREQ 1500000 (int) Returns current frequency

